<title>
DTC P0131 / P0132 / P2237 / P2243 / P2251/ P2626
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A1104025001">
<title>
DTC Detecting Condition and Trouble Area
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.872in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.303in"/>
<thead valign = "middle">
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" align = "center">
<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Trouble area
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0131: O2 Sensor Circuit Low Voltage
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Any of the following conditions is met. 
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (VM) circuit is lower than specified value for 10 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (UN) circuit is lower than specified value for 10 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (IA) circuit is lower than specified value for 10 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
A/F sensor and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0132: O2 Sensor Circuit High Voltage
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Any of the following conditions is met. 
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (VM) circuit is higher than specified value for 10 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (UN) circuit is higher than specified value for 10 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (IA) circuit is higher than specified value for 10 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P2237: O2 Sensor Positive Current Control Circuit / Open
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Any of the following conditions is met.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
A/F sensor signal stays within specified value for specified time.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (IP) circuit drops to lower than 1.7 V for 5 sec. during fuel-cut control.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (IP) circuit remains within specified range for 10 sec. even during enrichment / enleanment control.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P2243: O2 Sensor Reference Voltage Circuit / Open
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Any of the following conditions is met.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (UN) circuit is higher than 4.7 V for 5 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (UN) circuit is lower than 0.3 V for 5 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P2251: O2 Sensor Negative Current Control Circuit / Open
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (VM) circuit is 1.47 to 1.53 V for 5 sec.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P2626: O2 Sensor Pumping Current Trim Circuit / Open
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of A/F sensor signal (IA) circuit is higher than 4.8 V for 5 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
