<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A1104025003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<topic id = "AENCP70A1104025004">
<title>
P0131 / P0132
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Confirm that the following condition is met in this “DTC Confirmation Procedure”.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Battery voltage &#62; 10.7 V
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Run engine at idle speed for 30 sec.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A1104025005">
<title>
P2237 / P2626
</title>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Perform road test in a place where there is no traffic to prevent an accident.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Road test should be performed by two persons, a driver and a tester, on a level road.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Be sure to troubleshoot first unexpected DTCs previously detected in “DTC Confirmation Procedure”.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Confirm that the following conditions are met in this “DTC Confirmation Procedure”.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Battery voltage &#62; 10.7 V
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
DTC P0030, P0031, P0032, P0443, P0458 or P0459 is not detected.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and warm up to normal operating temperature.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Run engine at idle speed for 3 min.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive vehicle at 50 to 80 km/h (31 to 50 mile/h) constantly for 10 min. or more.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Release accelerator pedal, and keep vehicle coasting for 5 sec. with engine braking applied (fuel cut condition).
</ptxt>
</s1>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A1104025006">
<title>
P2243 / P2251
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Be sure to troubleshoot first unexpected DTCs previously detected in “DTC Confirmation Procedure”.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Confirm that the following conditions are met in this “DTC Confirmation Procedure”.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Battery voltage &#62; 10.7 V
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
DTC P0030, P0031 or P0032 is not detected.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and warm up to normal operating temperature.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Run engine at idle speed for 3 min.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</topic>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A1104025007">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENCP70A1104025008">
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A1104025009">
<question>
Was “Engine and Emission Control System Check” performed?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A1104001">Engine and Emission Control System Check</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A1104025010">
<title>
DTC check
</title>
<question>
Is there any DTC(s) other than P0131, P0132, P2237, P2243, P2251 and P2626?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to troubleshooting for applicable DTC.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A1104025011">
<title>
A/F sensor signal circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
When ignition is “OFF”, disconnect “C01” and “E01” connectors of ECM and A/F sensor connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to “C01” and “E01” connectors and A/F sensor connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance of “A2”, “A3”, “A4” and “A5” circuits: less than 1 Ω
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between each of “A2”, “A3”, “A4” and “A5” circuits and ground: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A2” circuit terminal and other terminal at A/F sensor connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A3” circuit terminal and other terminal at A/F sensor connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A4” circuit terminal and other terminal at A/F sensor connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A5” circuit terminal and other terminal at A/F sensor connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Voltage of “A2”, “A3”, “A4” and “A5” circuits: approx. 0 V (when ignition is “ON”)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Is check result OK?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 4.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A1104025012">
<title>
DTC recheck
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Replace A/F sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1306014"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Perform DTC confirmation procedure to check for DTCs.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is DTC P0131, P0132, P2237, P2243, P2251 and/or P2626 still detected?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace ECM and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
End.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
